                contained on its web site at any time without notice. {{ constant('site_title') }} does not, however, 
                make any commitment to update the materials.
            </p>

            <h2>Refund Policy</h2>
            <p class="mb-5">
                Once a product has been purchased by you, no right of cancellation or refund exists under the 
                Consumer Protection (Distance Selling) Regulations 2000 due to the electronic nature of our products. 
                Any refunds shall be at our sole and absolute discretion. You agree that under no circumstances 
                whatsoever shall you initiate any chargebacks via your payment provider. You agree that any payments
                made by you for any of our products are final and may not be charged back. We reserve the right 
                to alter any of our prices from time to time.
            </p>

            <p>By clicking agree below, you have read, understood, and agreed these terms.</p>
            
            <form action="{{ url('checkout') }}" method="post" class="w-100">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">I agree, continue</button>
                    <a href="{{ url('') }}" class="btn btn-link text-white-50">Abort Mission</a>
                    <input type="hidden" name="_token" value="{{ csrf_token }}" id="_token">
                </div>
            </form>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{%  endblock %}